oads/2021/05/TC-300x225.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" title="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TC-300x225.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TC-1024x767.jpg 1024w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TC-768x575.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TC-1536x1150.jpg 1536w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/TC.jpg 1603w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a> <div class="media-body"> <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/national/man-test-drives-car-never-to-be-seen-again"><h3>Man &#8220;test drives&#8221; car, never to be seen again</h3></a> <h6><span class="h_catagoris"><a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/national">Thailand News</a></span><span class="h_date">8 hours ago</span></h6> <p>Panya Muenknam, a 50 year old owner of the used car shop... </p> </div> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div></div></div></div> <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element view_more_btn" style="margin:0 0 40px;"> <div class="wpb_wrapper"> <p><a href="https://thethaiger.com/news">Read More Latest News</a></p> </div> </div> </div></div> <div class="vc_tta-panel" id="vid-news" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title"><a href="#vid-news" data-vc-accordion="" data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">VIDEO</span></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body" style=""><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"> <div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"> <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element"> <div class="wpb_wrapper"> <div class="hnews_list"> <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/national/thailand-news-today-500-covid-hospital-patients-escape-1-night-1-campaign-for-phuket-may-28"><div class="hnews_img"><img width="740" height="416" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-con